It’s no coincidence how much Ohio is being brought up tonight.

@POTUS knows it, I know it. We all know it: The road to winning our future goes straight through Ohio.

#SOTU

I’ve always been a big believer in the power of American innovation. 

To keep leading, we need policies that put our innovators and entrepreneurs in the digital asset space on top and give them clear guidelines needed to thrive.

@SecYellen must provide this much-needed clarity.

Thrilled to see thousands of manufacturing jobs get back in the hands of Ohio workers.

The best way we get this project moving is by passing the CHIPS Act immediately, which is what I’ve been calling on Congress to do for months. 

@SpeakerPelosi &amp; @LeaderHoyer: The time is now.

As students go #BackToSchool, it’s on ALL of us to help keep them safe. 

@CDCgov recommends ALL adults and children 12+ #GetVaccinated to help keep students healthy in the classroom. 

